OL,4,CMortgages refused for self-employed who
OL,5,Ctook Covid grants
OL,6, Some of Britain's biggest high street
OL,7, banks are refusing to give mortgages to
OL,8, self-employed people who received
OL,9, government grants during the pandemic.
OL,11,FMortgage brokers say those working in
OL,12,Fsectors like entertainment, hospitality
OL,13,Fand travel are the worst affected.
OL,15,FMany lenders spoken to by the BBC are
OL,16,Fnot accepting mortgage applications
OL,17,Ffrom people on furlough.
OL,19,FBrokers said that banks often see
OL,20,Fpeople who have received Covid-related
OL,21,Fgrants as high risk.
